'''Delta Unit''' was a military unit of the [[Alliance Special Forces/Legends|Alliance Special Forces]].

It was a part of infiltrator [[Scandium Team]], and the most notorious of its units, being highly respected by other Rebels. In particular, SpecForce [[Delta Team]] was named Delta to honor Delta Unit. Similarly, [[Delta Base]], in [[New Kisge]], was also named for [[Delta Unit]]

